{
  "id": "69b67b33562a0d562f7dd9e0",
  "title": "佐保川に　さばしる千鳥　よぐたちて　ながこゑ聞けば　いねがてなくに",
  "created": 1773566773,
  "updated": 1773567113,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b67c8800000000005c1772",
      "text": "佐保川に　さばしる千鳥　よぐたちて　ながこゑ聞けば　いねがてなくに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773567113,
      "updated": 1773567113
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b33562a0d562f7dd9e0",
      "text": "[萬葉集]（[万葉集]）に載っていた美しい和歌",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566773,
      "updated": 1773567113
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c8600000000005c1771",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773567110,
      "updated": 1773567110
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3400000000005c1758",
      "text": "佐保川爾　　　さほがはに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566773,
      "updated": 1773567110
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3d00000000005c1765",
      "text": "小驟千鳥　　　さばしるちどり",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566781,
      "updated": 1773566879
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3d00000000005c1766",
      "text": "夜三更而　　　よぐたちて",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566781,
      "updated": 1773566864
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3d00000000005c1767",
      "text": "爾音聞者　　　ながこゑきけば",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566781,
      "updated": 1773566880
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3d00000000005c1768",
      "text": "宿不難爾　　　いねがてなくに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566781,
      "updated": 1773566880
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3d00000000005c1769",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566781,
      "updated": 1773566781
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3400000000005c175e",
      "text": "[美しポイント]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566773,
      "updated": 1773566773
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3400000000005c175f",
      "text": "\t音は [57577] になっており、4 文字の漢字が並んでいる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566773,
      "updated": 1773566773
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3400000000005c1760",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566773,
      "updated": 1773566773
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3400000000005c1761",
      "text": "残念ポイント",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566773,
      "updated": 1773566773
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3400000000005c1762",
      "text": "\t漢字の中に万葉仮名が入っているため 4 文字の漢字と言い切れない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566773,
      "updated": 1773566874
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b3400000000005c1764",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566773,
      "updated": 1773566773
    }
  ]
}